OL,3,CE-bike fires on track to hit record
OL,4,Chigh this year
OL,6,FFires from e-bikes and e-scooters are
OL,7,Fon course to reach an all-time high in
OL,8,FLondon this year, new analysis shows.
OL,10,FLondon Fire Brigade (LFB) said it has
OL,11,Frecorded 165 fires involving the
OL,12,Fvehicles in 2025 up to September 28.
OL,14,FThat is an average of about 18 per
OL,15,Fmonth.
OL,17,FIf the trend continues until the end
OL,18,Fof December, London will surpass 200
OL,19,Fincidents in a single year for the
OL,20,Ffirst time.
