OL,6,FEden Abera Siem, 30, died in hospital
OL,7,Fafter being rescued by firefighters
OL,8,Fwhen a blaze ` which investigators
OL,9,Ffound was probably caused by the
OL,10,Ffailure of a charging e-bike battery `
OL,11,Fbroke out at her home on Lordship
OL,12,FLane, Wood Green on June 21.
OL,14,FThat was the fourth fatal e-bike fire
OL,15,Frecorded in the capital.
OL,17,FIn all four cases, the victim did not
OL,18,Fown or use the e-bike involved.
