OL,6,FPamela Oparaocha, LFB assistant
OL,7,Fcommissioner for prevention and
OL,8,Fprotection, said: "We continue to see
OL,9,Fthe devastating consequences of e-bike
OL,10,Fand e-scooter fires in London.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts are with the family of
OL,13,FEden as well as all those who have
OL,14,Fbeen impacted by fires in recent years.
OL,16,F"Fires involving e-bikes and e-
OL,17,Fscooters are worryingly common in
OL,18,FLondon.
