OL,6,F"Since the beginning of 2023, we have
OL,7,Fattended a fire, on average, every
OL,8,Fother day, and some of these fires
OL,9,Fhave destroyed homes and claimed
OL,10,Flives."
OL,12,FFires involving lithium batteries `
OL,13,Fwhich are used for e-bikes and e-
OL,14,Fscooters ` can spread rapidly and
OL,15,Fproduce a toxic vapour.
