OL,4,Chigh this year
OL,6,FProducts such as batteries, chargers
OL,7,Fand e-bike conversion kits bought from
OL,8,Fonline marketplaces are at greater
OL,9,Frisk of malfunctioning because they
OL,10,Fhave not been subjected to the same
OL,11,Flevel of regulation as high street
OL,12,Fshops, LFB said.
OL,14,FThe LFB said gig economy companies
OL,15,Fshould do more to raise awareness
OL,16,Fabout fire risks from e-bikes.
OL,18,FIt will be writing to delivery
OL,19,Fcompanies Uber Eats, Just Eat and
OL,20,FDeliveroo this week to ask them to
OL,21,Fshare safety advice with their riders.
