OL,6,FLesley Rudd, chief executive of
OL,7,Fcharity Electrical Safety First, said:
OL,8,F"We urge the Government to be brave
OL,9,Fand bold when considering what
OL,10,Fregulations they will introduce to
OL,11,Ftackle these fires, and continue to
OL,12,Fadvocate for the introduction of third-
OL,13,Fparty certification for e-bike
OL,14,Fbatteries to ensure they are safe
OL,15,Fbefore they can be sold on the UK
OL,16,Fmarket.
